Solnechnoye (; , Bata≈ü) is a rural locality (a selo) in Khasavyurtovsky District, Republic of Dagestan, Russia. Population:  There are 42 streets.
Geography
Solnechnoye is located 12&nbsp;km northwest of Khasavyurt (the district's administrative centre) by road. Nuradilovo is the nearest rural locality.
